<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Welcome to Our Grocery Store!</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333333;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
    }

    .header {
      background-color: #2e7d32;
      /* Green 800 */
      padding: 30px 20px;
      text-align: center;
      border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0;
    }

    .header h1 {
      color: #ffffff;
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 28px;
    }

    .content {
      padding: 30px 20px;
      background-color: #f5f5f5;
    }

    .footer {
      background-color: #e8f5e9;
      /* Light green 50 */
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
      border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #666666;
    }

    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 12px 24px;
      background-color: #43a047;
      /* Green 600 */
      color: white !important;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 4px;
      font-weight: bold;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }

    .divider {
      height: 1px;
      background-color: #e0e0e0;
      margin: 25px 0;
    }

    .highlight {
      color: #2e7d32;
      font-weight: bold;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <div class="header">
    <h1>Welcome to Grocery Store Groceries!</h1>
  </div>

  <div class="content">
    <p>Hello <span class="highlight">{{firstName}}</span>,</p>

    <p>We're thrilled to welcome you to Grocery Store Groceries! Your account was successfully created on <span
        class="highlight">{{joinedAt}}</span>.</p>

    <p>At Grocery Store, we're committed to bringing you the freshest produce and highest quality groceries delivered
      right to your doorstep.</p>

    <center>
      <a href="https://yourgrocerystore.com/shop" class="button">Start Shopping Now</a>
    </center>

    <div class="divider"></div>

    <h3>Here's what you can do with your account:</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>Browse our fresh produce and grocery selections</li>
      <li>Schedule deliveries at your convenience</li>
      <li>Track your orders in real-time</li>
      <li>Earn rewards with every purchase</li>
    </ul>

    <p>As a welcome gift, here's a special discount code for your first order:</p>

    <center>
      <div
        style="background-color: #e8f5e9; padding: 15px; border-radius: 4px; display: inline-block; font-size: 18px; font-weight: bold;">
        WELCOME10
      </div>
      <p style="font-size: 14px;">(Get 10% off your first order of KES 500 or more)</p>
    </center>
  </div>

  <div class="footer">
    <p>If you didn't create this account, please contact us immediately at <a
        href="mailto:support@groceryStore.com">support@groceryStore.com</a>.</p>
    <p>&copy; {{year}} Grocery Store Groceries. All rights reserved.</p>
    <p>
      <a href="https://yourgrocerystore.com/privacy">Privacy Policy</a> |
      <a href="https://yourgrocerystore.com/terms">Terms of Service</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</body>

</html>